{
  "channel": "{{local_var.channel_id}}",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "text": { "type": "plain_text", "emoji": true, "text": "WAF Attack (SQLi / XSS / Traversal) — shop.soledrop.co (HIGH)" }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*A single source is attacking the SoleDrop webstore (SQL injection / XSS / path-traversal) — Cloudflare WAF ML flagged the requests.*\n\n*Source IP:* `{{local_var.src_ip}}`  (geo: {{Function.DEFAULT(virustotal-search-ip.body.data.attributes.country, "N/A")}})\n*VirusTotal:* {{Function.DEFAULT(virustotal-search-ip.body.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.malicious, "N/A")}} engines malicious\n*AbuseIPDB:* {{Function.DEFAULT(abuseipdb-check-ip.body.data.abuseConfidenceScore, "N/A")}}/100 abuse confidence\n*WAF attack requests on shop.soledrop.co:* *{{local_var.attack_requests}}*\n*Worst WAF ML attack score (1=most malicious):* {{local_var.worst_score}}\n*Sample URI:* `{{local_var.sample_uri}}`  (method {{local_var.method}})\n*ATT&CK:* T1190" }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*Before you block:* confirm `{{local_var.src_ip}}` is not an authorized vulnerability scan / pentest or a security researcher — sanctioned scanners also trip the WAF ML score. If it is sanctioned, Dismiss." }
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*Alert:* <{{Function.GET_MANAGEMENT_URL()}}/incidents/unified-alerts?alertId={{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}|{{singularity-response-trigger.data.name}}>" }
    },
    {
      "type": "actions",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "button",
          "text": { "type": "plain_text", "emoji": true, "text": "Block at Cloudflare" },
          "style": "primary",
          "value": "approved"
        },
        {
          "type": "button",
          "text": { "type": "plain_text", "emoji": true, "text": "Dismiss — False Positive" },
          "style": "danger",
          "value": "dismissed"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

{
  "channel": "{{local_var.channel_id}}",
  "ts": "{{send-interactive-message.body.ts}}",
  "text": "`{{local_var.src_ip}}` was blocked at the Cloudflare edge (IP Access Rule) by {{wait-for-slack.body.user.username}}.\n\n*Alert:* <{{Function.GET_MANAGEMENT_URL()}}/incidents/unified-alerts?alertId={{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}|{{singularity-response-trigger.data.name}}>"
}

{
  "channel": "{{local_var.channel_id}}",
  "ts": "{{send-interactive-message.body.ts}}",
  "text": "Dismissed as false positive (e.g. shared corporate egress / NAT). No block applied. Alert: <{{Function.GET_MANAGEMENT_URL()}}/incidents/unified-alerts?alertId={{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}|{{singularity-response-trigger.data.name}}>"
}

{
  "action": "block",
  "expression": "ip.src eq {{local_var.src_ip}} and http.host eq \"{{local_var.target_host}}\"",
  "description": "OneFlare web-attacks host-scoped block \u2014 alert {{singularity-response-trigger.data.id}}",
  "enabled": true
}
